stories.text:
Hi hunters, I feel like making something good for as many people as I can, and I think HN Community is the right place to help other founders/launchers. You can ask me here or email me at janetjujefesko@gmail.com to send me your beta product or JUST share your idea, and I am going to give you my honest and constructive feedback about it.

A little bit about me: I have participated in an accelerator program Founder Institute 2019 batch, and I won the second place reward graduating as the only solo female founder.

My work experience is as a UXD and PM at famous product companies in my country.
